    public abstract class AbstractTest

        public void executeBeforeSuite(org.testng.ITestContext context)
        Before test suite execution: initialized log4j properties, Rest-Assured base URL and Test-Executer logging context. Also it clears reports folder if reports history is more than configuration attribute - 'max_screen_history'.
        Parameters:
        context - TestNG test context
